import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    age = data['age']
    plt.hist(age, bins=20, color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.axvline(age.mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Mean Age: {age.mean():.2f}')
    plt.axvline(age.median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Median Age: {age.median():.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of age in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.bar(data.index, data['height'])
    plt.title('What is the average height of individuals in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    plt.axhline(data['height'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f"Average Height: {data['height'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.scatter(data['age'], data['height'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Age')
    ax.set_ylabel('Height')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between age and height in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    name_counts = data['name'].value_counts()
    plt.bar(name_counts.index, name_counts.values)
    plt.title('What is the most common name in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    plt.axhline(y=name_counts.max(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Most common name: {name_counts.idxmax()} ({name_counts.max():.2f})')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    name = 'John'
    age = data[data['name'] == name]['age']
    plt.hist(age, bins=10, color='blue', alpha=0.5)
    plt.axvline(age.mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Mean Age: {age.mean():.2f}')
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.title(f"What is the age distribution for individuals with the name {name}?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
